</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/liberf0rce" rel="author">liberforce</a> (<a href="http://blog.freeside.fr">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-26T22:47:39+01:00"><span class="date">le 26/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 22:47</span></time>.
