<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/ideefixe" rel="author">idéefixe</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-27T22:13:49+01:00"><span class="date">le 27/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 22:13</span></time>.
